</tr><tr><td class="sidebar-content">
<div class="sidebar-list mw-collapsible mw-collapsed"><div class="sidebar-list-title"><a href="/wiki/The_Church_of_Jesus_Christ_of_Latter-day_Saints" title="The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints">Latter-day Saints</a></div><div class="sidebar-list-content mw-collapsible-content"><a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young" title="Brigham Young">Brigham Young</a>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<a href="/wiki/List_of_Brigham_Young%27s_wives" title="List of Brigham Young&#39;s wives">Wives of Brigham Young</a>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<a href="/wiki/Latter_Day_Saint_polygamy_in_the_late-19th_century" title="Latter Day Saint polygamy in the late-19th century">Late-19th century Mormon polygamy</a>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<a href="/wiki/Mormon_colonies_in_Mexico" title="Mormon colonies in Mexico">Mormon colonies in Mexico</a>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<a href="/wiki/1890_Manifesto" title="1890 Manifesto">1890 Manifesto</a>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<a href="/wiki/Reed_Smoot_hearings" title="Reed Smoot hearings">Reed Smoot hearings</a>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<a href="/wiki/Second_Manifesto" title="Second Manifesto">1904 Manifesto</a></div></div></td>
</tr><tr><td class="sidebar-content">
