</tr><tr><td class="sidebar-content">
<div class="sidebar-list mw-collapsible mw-collapsed"><div class="sidebar-list-title">Case law</div><div class="sidebar-list-content mw-collapsible-content"><i><a href="/wiki/Reynolds_v._United_States" title="Reynolds v. United States">Reynolds v. US</a></i>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<i><a href="/wiki/Angus_M._Cannon#Polygamy_prosecution" title="Angus M. Cannon">Cannon v. US</a></i>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<i><a href="/wiki/Clawson_v._United_States" title="Clawson v. United States">Clawson v. US</a></i>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<i><a href="/wiki/Davis_v._Beason" title="Davis v. Beason">Davis v. Beason</a></i>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<i><a href="/wiki/Late_Corp._of_the_Church_of_Jesus_Christ_of_Latter-Day_Saints_v._United_States" title="Late Corp. of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-Day Saints v. United States">Late Corp. of the LDS Church v. US</a></i>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<i><a href="/wiki/Cleveland_v._United_States_(1946)" title="Cleveland v. United States (1946)">Cleveland v. US</a></i>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<i><a href="/wiki/Brown_v._Buhman" title="Brown v. Buhman">Brown v. Buhman</a></i>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<a href="/wiki/List_of_polygamy_court_cases" title="List of polygamy court cases">List of polygamy court cases</a></div></div></td>
</tr><tr><td class="sidebar-content">
<div class="sidebar-list mw-collapsible mw-collapsed"><div class="sidebar-list-title"><a href="/wiki/Category:Mormonism_and_polygamy" title="Category:Mormonism and polygamy">Related articles</a></div><div class="sidebar-list-content mw-collapsible-content"><a href="/wiki/Celestial_marriage" title="Celestial marriage">Celestial marriage</a>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<a href="/wiki/Freedom_of_religion_in_the_United_States" title="Freedom of religion in the United States">Freedom of religion in the US</a>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<a href="/wiki/Legal_status_of_polygamy" class="mw-redirect" title="Legal status of polygamy">Legal status of polygamy</a>&#160;&#8226;&#32;<a href="/wiki/List_of_Latter_Day_Saint_practitioners_of_plural_marriage" title="List of Latter Day Saint practitioners of plural marriage">List of practitioners</a>
