<ul><li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBachman1978" class="citation journal cs1"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Danel_W._Bachman&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Danel W. Bachman (page does not exist)">Bachman, Danel W.</a> (1978). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20081221221652/http://content.lib.utah.edu/u/?%2Fjmh%2C10134">"New Light on an Old Hypothesis: The Ohio Origins of the Revelation on Eternal Marriage"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Journal_of_Mormon_History" class="mw-redirect" title="Journal of Mormon History">Journal of Mormon History</a></i>. <b>5</b>: 19–32. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://content.lib.utah.edu/u?/jmh,10134">the original</a> on December 21, 2008.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Mormon+History&amp;rft.atitle=New+Light+on+an+Old+Hypothesis%3A+The+Ohio+Origins+of+the+Revelation+on+Eternal+Marriage&amp;rft.volume=5&amp;rft.pages=19-32&amp;rft.date=1978&amp;rft.aulast=Bachman&amp;rft.aufirst=Danel+W.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcontent.lib.utah.edu%2Fu%3F%2Fjmh%2C10134&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMormonism+and+polygamy" class="Z3988"></span></li>
